criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Students approved in the discipline related to nursing care for adult and elderly
             patients;

          -  Aged over 18 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Who have experience in the health field (firefighters and nursing technicians, among
             others);

          -  Members of the Health Simulation League;

          -  Those who do not complete all stages of the research.
